Subject: [PATCH] PCI: pci-bridge-emul: Create per-bridge copy of register
 behavior
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bnc#1012628
